elocity\ndispersion. This simple scenario generates most of the properties of the\ngalaxies but not flat rotation-curves. Finally we attempt to weigh up its pros\nand cons as a viable theory of galaxy formation and conclude that it is much\nsuperior to the Hierarchical model when it comes to fitting most observations.\nAt the very least it deserves further critical evaluation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Mar 2017 16:15:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 6 Mar 2017 12:57:39 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 8 Mar 2017 10:09:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-09"}
