{19}$ eV\nand heavier nuclei up to $10^{20-21}$ eV.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Mar 2017 17:13:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 3 Mar 2017 18:58:18 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 6 Jun 2017 22:36:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-09"}
