l off\nthe center of the WD. The rate of LSD-induced explosions matches the observed\nrate of Type Ia supernovae.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Mar 2017 17:13:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 3 Mar 2017 18:55:19 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 29 May 2017 17:58:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-02"}
