P) algorithm on graphs of\nbounded treewidth for the same extension. In addition, we propose a general\nprocedure of deriving XP algorithms on graphs on bounded treewidth via\nformulation as Constraint Satisfaction Problems (CSP). This shows an alternate\napproach as compared to standard dynamic programming formulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Mar 2017 23:15:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Jun 2017 19:33:03 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 6 Dec 2018 15:56:14 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 9 Oct 2019 17:14:13 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 3 Dec 2019 13:57:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-19"}
