r steadily lose their spin. More frequent\nmergers, accompanied by an inability to regain spin, lead massive ellipticals\nto lose most of ordered rotation and transition from FRs to SRs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Mar 2017 23:26:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 Mar 2017 21:11:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-10"}
