ar. In 1997 the meteorological drought greatest damage\noccurs in the Coello River basin generally concentrated in the middle and lower\npart of the basin, with a maximum intensity of SPI -2,57.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Mar 2017 16:52:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-08"}
